data.description: Beautiful and well-maintained Maronda-CONCRETE BLOCK home in quaint Newberry Corners! Built in 2018, this home offers 3 bedrooms, 2 full baths, an office and a flex room that can easily be a 4th bedroom, sprawled on 2000 sq ft of H/C spaces! Premium and stylish light fixtures adorn this home! Large and gorgeous kitchen with generous amount of cabinetry and solid counter space! It boasts of stainless steel appliances, an island, coffee bar area plus a nook area when you come in from the garage! Plenty of natural light feeding the already open lay out! The kitchen opens up to the dining and great room, making it one great hub for family and friends to gather! A vestibule leads you to the master suite with walk in closet and bath that offers a garden tub and walk-in shower! Find the flex room to the left of the foyer and 2 guest bedrooms + office on the other side! The guest bathroom has double vanities! Check out the storage space behind the laundry door! Low HOA! Close to the coming-soon Publix and zoned schools Newberry Elem, Oakview Middle and Newberry High School! Call now!
